<p>The three-time world cyclo-cross champion Zdenek Stybar is return to CX this winter, and he'll be racing aboard a very special custom painted Specialized CruX. Read all about it <a href="https://road.cc/content/tech-news/268433-zdenek-stybar-returns-cyclo-cross-and-his-new-specialized-crux-gorgeous">here</a>. </p>
